<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Borrows</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>

<div class="home-float">
		<!-- AddThis Button BEGIN -->
			<div class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style addthis_16x16_style home-share">
				<a class="addthis_button_email"></a>
				<a class="addthis_button_facebook"></a>
				<a class="addthis_button_twitter"></a>
				<a class="addthis_button_linkedin"></a>
				<a class="addthis_button_google_plusone_share"></a>
				<a class="addthis_button_pinterest_share"></a>
			</div>
			<script type="text/javascript">var addthis_config = {"data_track_addressbar":true};</script>
			<script type="text/javascript" src="//s7.addthis.com/js/300/addthis_widget.js#pubid=ra-530ee7046fcbd127"></script>
		<!-- AddThis Button END -->
		<h1>Borrowing > Buying</h1>
		</br>
		<p>Need something just the once or twice? We know: you don't want to compare or to browse, you just want <b>it</b>. We help you find what you need from your friends. We make sure to only ping the folks who have what you need, because we hate spam too!</p>
		</br>
		<div class="col-xs-6">
			<a href="<%= new_signup_path %>" class="btn btn-primary btn-large btn-block home-btn" role="button">Cool, sign me up to try it!</a>
			<p><i>If you refer the <b>86th</b> person to sign up, both you and your friend who signs up will get a gift!</i></p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-xs-6">
			<a href="<%= new_request_path %>" class="btn btn-primary btn-large btn-block home-btn" role="button">I need to borrow something today!</a>
			<p><i>We're inviting small groups of users at a time, though if you have any ideas now <a href="mailto:jdong8@gmail.com?subject='Thoughts on sharing'" style="color: grey"><u>please share them with us!</u></i></p>
		</div>
</div>

<div id="HomeCarousel" class="carousel slide">
	<ol class="carousel-indicators">
		<li data-target="#HomeCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
		<li data-target="#HomeCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
		<li data-target="#HomeCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
		<li data-target="#HomeCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
	</ol>

	<div class="carousel-inner">
		
		<div class="item active">
			<div class ="fill" style="background-image: url('http://hdwallpapersci.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/dsfsdf1.jpg');">
				<div class="carousel-caption">
					<h2>Because you deserve a weekend adventure off-the-grid</h2>
					<h4>Step 1 - Borrow a tent, bag, pad, pack</h4>
					<h4>Step 2 - Begin your epic journey!</h4>
			    </div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="item">
			<div class ="fill" style="background-image: url('http://www.wallsave.com/wallpapers/1920x1080/beachvolleyball/414822/beachvolleyball-beach-volleyball-serving-jump-hd-and-414822.jpg');">
				<div class="carousel-caption">
					<h2>Because a group of your friends are all free on a Sunday</h2>
					<h4>Step 1 - Borrow a ball & net</h4>
					<h4>Step 2 - Head to the nearest beach!</h4>
			    </div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="item">
			<div class ="fill" style="background-image: url('http://img.wallpaperstock.net:81/beautiful-furniture-wallpapers_17618_1920x1080.jpg');">
				<div class="carousel-caption">
					<h2>Because it's nice to have something to show for your work</h2>
					<h4>Step 1 - Borrow some tools</h4>
					<h4>Step 2 - Recreate your world!</h4>
			    </div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="item">
			<div class ="fill" style="background-image: url('http://www.wallpapersdesign.net/wallpapers/2013/12/Ski-Jump-1080x1920.jpg');">
				<div class="carousel-caption">
					<h2>Because it might be the closest you'll ever get to flying</h2>
					<h4>Step 1 - Borrow warm layers & protective gear</h4>
					<h4>Step 2 - Hit the slopes!</h4>
			    </div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
		
	<a class="left carousel-control" href="#HomeCarousel" data-slide="prev">
    	<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
  	</a>
  	<a class="right carousel-control" href="#HomeCarousel" data-slide="next">
   		<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
  	</a>

</div>

</div>



